      "code_id": "4941ff22-66c0-4e84-af9f-2cc14225ee54",
      "code_content": "word = input()\nstart_index = input()\nstart_index = int(start_index)\n\nend_index = input()\nend_index = int(end_index)\n\npart = word[start_index:end_index + 1]\nprint(part)",
